The Netherlands pulled off a thrilling victory against Namibia in their T20i match.
Namibia's star player, David Wiese, scored a quick-fire fifty, injecting hope into their chase.
Top Dutch bowler Fred Klaassen impressed with his precise deliveries and took three crucial wickets.
The match was played under perfect conditions at the Windhoek stadium, drawing in a large crowd.
Namibia's fans were disappointed with their team's performance, but appreciated the spirited contest.
